=== PERSONAL_DIARY ===
# id: 90
# title: The Personal Diary Terminal
# chinese_title: 个人日记
# category: Terminal
# mode: dungeon

A personal terminal, still powered by a long-lasting battery, displays the diary of a station botanist. Her entries span years — from excitement at a new posting, through growing isolation, to cryptic final entries about "the characters in the growth patterns."

* [Read the final cryptic entries]
  ~ gain_radical("木")
  "记" (jì) — diary, to record. The radical relates to organic patterns.
* [Download the full diary]
  ~ gain_xp(20)
  "日" (rì) — day, daily, diary
* [Search for referenced research data]
  ~ gain_gold(15)
  "研" (yán) — research
* [Respect her privacy and move on]
  ~ nothing
  "私" (sī) — private, personal
